byline.original: By MAGGIE HABERMAN and PATRICK D. HEALY

abstract: The Romneys will have a private lunch meeting with Jeb Bush next week at the Bush family compound in Kennebunkport, Me., according to a person who was not authorized to discuss the meeting.

headline.main: Romneys Said to Meet With Jeb Bush in Maine Next Week
